Diamond::
She sighed, "yes commander. I will. Right away."
She took the jar and left her room. She went to the main lab and 
walked in. She saw the mongoose working and puttering around the lab.
"Zardus tole me to give this DNA sample to you. It's KitKat's."

Squizzy::
"Oh wonderful.  I'll get on it right away."  She walked over to 
Diamond and got the sample from her. She walked over and poured the 
contents of the jar into the DNA scanner.  It wuld take a while, but 
she would ave a good clone when she was done.
